```{r}
library(readr)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
```

```{r}
data <- read_csv("data/data.csv")

data_select <- data %>%
  filter(Entity == "Australia")
```

```{r}
data_select %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = Year, y = `Population - Sex: all - Age: all - Variant: estimates`))+
  geom_line()+
  labs(title = "Population of Australia", 
       x = "Year", 
       y = "Population")
```
